snippet.title: Rainbow Six SMOL | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Defuse bombs, free hostages and crush enemies in this unexpected spin on the "Rainbow Six" franchise. Assemble the best squad, save the (smol) world!

Play Rainbow Six SMOL on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81622983

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 260 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
